# Bounds the Dockerfile's `COPY *.mjs ./`. The glob is deliberate — naming files
# individually drifts silently and the job would die at ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND on
# Fargate, after the sweep already claimed the row — but this repo has a strong
# habit of dropping scratch probes next to the thing they debug
# (veo-automations/probe-mes-v2.mjs, capture-pm-full.mjs, spiideo-health-fetch.mjs),
# and an unbounded glob would ship one into the production image.
__tests__
node_modules
*.test.mjs
*.test.ts
buildspec.yml
